OL,5,G1325 They Rode West
OL,6,     F(1954) Tough western. A cavalry
OL,7,     Fdoctor (Robert Francis) discovers
OL,8,     Fa Native American tribe is dying
OL,9,     Fof malaria, but his by-the-book
OL,10,     Fcaptain (Phil Carey) refuses to
OL,11,     Fallow their treatment.
OL,12,G1505 The Sheriff of Fractured Jaw
OL,13,     F(1959) Comedy western with Kenneth
OL,14,     FMore. An English gunsmith decides
OL,15,     Fthe Wild West is the best market
OL,16,     Ffor his wares, but little does he
OL,17,     Fexpect to end up sheriff of a
OL,18,     Flawless frontier town.
